{
  "stem": "12255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were driven out of their hometowns, and they were herded into ghettos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were herded into trains, taken to Auschwitz and so on, and then onto Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bergen-Belsen became overcrowded, because the Russians were advancing so quickly, and the-- and the Germans didn't want the Russians to see what they had done.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they pushed thousands and thousands from those camps which were nearer to where the Russians were advancing, and marched them for days and days into Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is why it was bursting at the seams.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the task ahead of us, I saw simply is to help them to return to normalcy, to live a reasonably normal life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this began to be realized in some very small measure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, I must say, pay tribute to some of the British authorities, who did outstanding work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a brigadier, I can't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know later he was a great rugby man, because he's been to South Africa a number of times.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a medical man, and he established a hospital for those who were in need of treatment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, what happened then was that the old camp, which was ridden with all sort of infectious diseases--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every time you went in or out, you had to be sprayed with-- with-- I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "White powder to kill the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Disinfectant.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and they decided to burn down the old camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And first, they transferred all the survivors to a nearby Panzer barracks, very, very modern, and with a very nice facility.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, it was for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At least they had a clean room, and they had-- they had certain toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
